<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PeruTM3.1">
<l>meyyil vāḻkkaiyai meyyeṉak koḷḷumiv</l>
<l>vaiyan taṉṉoṭuṅ kūṭuva tillaiyāṉ</l>
<l>aiya ṉēyaraṅkā veṉṟa ḻaikkiṉṟēṉ</l>
<l>maiyal koṇṭoḻin tēṉeṉtaṉ mālukkē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>There will be no joining, for me,</l>
<l>with this earth that takes unreal life to be real.</l>
<l>I cry out saying, ‘O Master! O Raṅga!’</l>
<l>I have ended up bearing mad [love] for my own Māl.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
